RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT B.CONTRACT_REF_NO,A.USER_REF_NO FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT A,LBTBS_CONTRACT_DISCLOSURE B WHERE A.CONTRACT_REF_NO=B.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND B.AUTH_STAT='A' AND B.RECORD_STAT='O' AND A.MODULE_CODE IN ('OL') AND A.PRODUCT_CODE IN (SELECT PRODUCT_CODE FROM LBTMS_PROD_DISCLOSURE) AND A.BRANCH= GLOBAL.CURRENT_BRANCH

SELECT A.DISCLOSURE_CODE, B.DISCLOSURE_DESCRIPTION FROM LBTBS_CONTRACT_DISC_MASTER A, LBTMS_DISCLOSURE B WHERE A.DISCLOSURE_CODE = B.DISCLOSURE_CODE AND A.CONTRACT_REF_NO =? AND B.RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND B.AUTH_STAT = 'A'
